title: Tom Bilyeu AMA on Crushing Your Goals Like A CEO
description: Tom Bilyeu does a rapid fire AMA (ask me anything) pulled from the 24 hour, Facebook Live Impactathon. Topics include: * How to stick to your goals. * Dealing with people who have a fixed mindset. * Tom's views on Stoicism. * The Difference between imagining your goals vs. executing on them. * When to delegate tasks to others. * How to grow your team with effective leadership. *And much more...
